---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ContactCTA from '../../components/ContactCTA.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Audible — Jason Ferrara" transparentNav>
  <article class="case-study">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <img src="/images/audible/audible_logo_2C_rgb.png" alt="Audible" class="hero-logo animate" />
          <h1 class="animate" style="--delay: 0.1s">Modernizing Audible's Platform Experience</h1>
          <div class="hero-meta animate" style="--delay: 0.15s">
            <span class="meta-detail">UX Director &mdash; Systems &amp; Information Architecture</span>
            <span class="meta-sep">/</span>
            <span class="meta-detail">2020&ndash;2022</span>
          </div>
          <p class="animate" style="--delay: 0.2s">Audible was entering a critical inflection point. Member sentiment described the app as stale and stagnant, discovery felt constrained, and Audible Originals, a key differentiator, accounted for just 10% of listening time.</p>
          <p class="animate" style="--delay: 0.25s">At the same time, large-scale UX updates were historically slow, with features taking six to nine months to ship due to organizational silos and competing priorities.</p>
          <p class="animate" style="--delay: 0.3s">I co-led the definition of a product experience North Star to reposition Audible as a premium, personalized media platform, then built a cross-functional operating model and experimentation roadmap to deliberately test into that vision at speed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-visual animate" style="--delay: 0.2s">
          <img src="/images/audible/Audible_hero.png" alt="Audible app redesign — home experience" class="hero-device-img" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Defining the North Star -->
    <section class="cs-section cs-section-alt container">
      <div class="section-top-grid">
        <div class="section-top-copy">
          <span class="cs-label animate">North Star Vision</span>
          <h2 class="cs-heading animate" style="--delay: 0.1s">Moving Fast &amp; Making It Real</h2>
          <p class="cs-intro animate" style="--delay: 0.15s">In partnership with Product leadership, we established a clear ambition for the platform. Audible needed to present itself as a premium media experience, elevate first-party Originals without eroding member trust, improve clarity in personalization and discovery, modernize the visual language across native surfaces, and create a foundation that could support future business model expansion. Rather than attempt a sweeping redesign, we sequenced high-impact experiments to validate each pillar of that direction before scaling.</p>
          <p class="cs-intro cs-intro-impact animate" style="--delay: 0.2s">These gains were achieved through a series of lightweight multivariate testing and staged rollout aligned to the North Star vision over a single quarter.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="impact-grid-side">
          <div class="impact-metric animate">
            <span class="impact-delta">+14%</span>
            <span class="impact-label">Originals Listening</span>
          </div>
          <div class="impact-metric animate" style="--delay: 0.1s">
            <span class="impact-delta">+3.5%</span>
            <span class="impact-label">Revenue Increase</span>
          </div>
          <div class="impact-metric animate" style="--delay: 0.2s">
            <span class="impact-delta">36%</span>
            <span class="impact-label">Faster Feature Delivery</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <span class="cs-sublabel animate">Focus Areas</span>

      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature animate">
          <div class="feature-image">
            <img src="/images/audible/Vision.png" alt="Audible North Star experimentation framework" />
          </div>
          <h3>North Star to Structured Experimentation</h3>
          <p>Translated high-level experience principles into testable hypotheses across App Home, product detail pages, and discovery modules. Paired qualitative research with in-production multivariate testing to validate direction before committing to full system overhaul.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature animate" style="--delay: 0.1s">
          <div class="feature-image">
            <img src="/images/audible/Home.png" alt="Audible premium App Home redesign" />
          </div>
          <h3>Premium App Home Revitalization and Scalable Delivery</h3>
          <p>Redesigned the App Home experience to elevate Originals and modernize presentation while preserving personalization clarity. Rather than pursue a full component rebuild with a projected 22-week timeline, I led a reduced-scope experimentation path that brought validated updates to market in eight weeks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature animate" style="--delay: 0.2s">
          <div class="feature-image">
            <img src="/images/audible/Teams.png" alt="Audible cross-functional squad model" />
          </div>
          <h3>Organizational Realignment for Velocity</h3>
          <p>Partnered with Product and Engineering leadership to launch Audible Tech's first fully dedicated cross-functional squad. Established singular roadmap ownership, standardized ceremonies, and tighter collaboration loops.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <ContactCTA variant="case-study" />

  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
  html {
    background: #f7f5f2 !important;
  }
</style>

<style>
  /* Page Gradient */
  .case-study {
    position: relative;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0e6db 0%, #f4f0eb 35%, #eef1f5 65%, #f7f5f2 100%);
  }

  .case-study::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -100vh;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    background: #f0e6db;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding: 4.5rem 0 5rem;
    padding-top: calc(4.5rem + var(--nav-height));
  }

  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-logo {
    height: 84px;
    width: auto;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
  }

  .meta-detail {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .meta-sep {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-border);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-copy > p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* Hero Visual */
  .hero-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-device-img {
    width: 80%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  /* Section */
  .cs-section {
    padding-top: 5rem;
    padding-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .cs-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cs-heading {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .cs-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .cs-intro-secondary {
    margin-top: -2.5rem;
  }

  .cs-intro-followup {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .north-star-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 42rem;
  }

  .north-star-list li {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .north-star-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-text);
  }

  .cs-section-alt {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  /* Side-by-side intro + metrics */
  .section-top-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .section-top-copy .cs-intro {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .section-top-copy .cs-intro-impact {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .impact-grid-side {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2.5rem 2rem;
    padding-left: 4rem;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .cs-sublabel {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  /* Features Grid */
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-image {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .feature-image img {
    height: 480px;
    width: auto;
    max-width: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .feature h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .feature p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .feature-aside {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  /* Impact */
  .impact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3.5rem 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .impact-grid-3col {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  }

  .impact-grid-4col {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  }

  .cs-intro-impact {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .impact-metric {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .impact-delta {
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 4.8vw, 3.6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .impact-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .impact-range {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 5rem 0 3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .section-top-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .impact-grid-side {
      padding-left: 0;
      border-left: none;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .impact-grid {
      gap: 2.5rem 2rem;
    }

    .impact-grid-3col {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .impact-grid-4col {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
